<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.234349>
    dc:description "FIGURES 11 – 18. Baldratia karamae. 11. Head. 12. Male distal flagellomeres. 13. Female distal flagellomeres. 14. Wing. 15. The distal tarsomere. 16. Genitalia (the mediobasal lobes are shown as would be seen if cerci were removed, setulae are not shown). 17. Female terminal abdominal segments. 18. Ovipositor." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/234349/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

